com.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.frame.chat

Class ChatIntegratedPlayer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.frame.VideoPlayer
      • com.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.frame.chat.ChatIntegratedPlayer

  • public class ChatIntegratedPlayer
extends VideoPlayer
    A VLCJ integrated player used to play videos in Minecraft. The library uses a callback for the specific function from native libraries. It renders it in chat.
